title.narrative: APHIA Plus Northern Arid Lands (NAL) IMARISHA

description.narrative: (Kenya): APHIAplus IMARISHA will support the integration of HIV, tuberculosis, family planning (FP) and reproductive, maternal, neonatal and child health, nutrition, water, and sanitation interventions in the Northern Arid Lands of Kenya.Using FY2015 funds, this activity will:-HIV prevention, care and treatment-Antenatal care, skilled birth attendance, emergency obstetric care and essential newborn care-Prevention and management of diarrheal diseases through household and school based hygiene practices and total community led sanitation. Oral rehydration solution (ORS)/Zinc scale up will continue in facilities-Routine immunization ?-Essential nutrition actions and skills in infant and young child feeding -Forecasting and quantification of commodities at facility level-FP skills building, mentorship, counseling and provision of quality services by health providers and community health workers
